snippet.title: drewstarr71
snippet.description:
LAWFUL REBELLION!   I DO NOT CONSENT!   ΜΟΛΩΝ ΛΑΒΕ   I am a political atheist!

When Injustice becomes law, Resistance﻿ becomes duty!


Sheeple willful ignorance: (noun) - The practice or act of intentional and blatant avoidance, disregard or disagreement with facts, empirical evidence and well-founded arguments because they oppose or contradict your own existing personal beliefs.
